              {
                "type": "glossaryTooltip",
                "attrs": {
                  "term": "elderflower cordial",
                  "termId": "cmpbcz09r0000h8v4ns8b2ynp"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": " appears in three places in this cake: brushed onto the sponge layers as a soaking syrup, stirred into the cream filling, and thinned with lemon juice for the icing. Each layer reinforces the elderflower flavour without overpowering the lemon.",
